VYQUr'a 'aL-MShH VYDBUr YHVH 'aLYV M'aHL MV'yD L'aMUr.
DBUr 'aL-BNY YShUr'aL V'aMUrTh 'aLHM 'aDM KY-YQUrYB MKM QUrBN LYHVH MN- HBHMH MN-HBQUr VMN-HTSh'aN ThQUrYBV 'aTh-QUrBNKM.
'aM-'yLH QUrBNV MN-HBQUr ZKUr ThMYM YQUrYBNV 'aL-PhThCh 'aHL MV'yD YQUrYB 'aThV LUrTShNV LPhNY YHVH.
VSMK YDV 'yL Ur'aSh H'yLH VNUrTShH LV LKPhUr 'yLYV.
VShChT 'aTh-BN HBQUr LPhNY YHVH VHQUrYBV BNY 'aHUrN HKHNYM 'aTh-HDM VZUrQV 'aTh-HDM 'yL-HMZBCh SBYB 'aShUr-PhThCh 'aHL MV'yD.
VHPhShYT 'aTh-H'yLH VNThCh 'aThH LNThChYH.
VNThNV BNY 'aHUrN HKHN 'aSh 'yL-HMZBCh V'yUrKV 'yTShYM 'yL-H'aSh.
V'yUrKV BNY 'aHUrN HKHNYM 'aTh HNThChYM 'aTh-HUr'aSh V'aTh-HPhDUr 'yL-H'yTShYM 'aShUr 'yL-H'aSh 'aShUr 'yL-HMZBCh.
VQUrBV VKUr'yYV YUrChTSh BMYM VHQTYUr HKHN 'aTh-HKL HMZBChH 'yLH 'aShH UrYCh- NYChVCh LYHVH.
V'aM-MN-HTSh'aN QUrBNV MN-HKShBYM 'aV MN-H'yZYM L'yLH ZKUr ThMYM YQUrYBNV.
VShChT 'aThV 'yL YUrK HMZBCh TShPhNH LPhNY YHVH VZUrQV BNY 'aHUrN HKHNYM 'aTh-DMV 'yL-HMZBCh SBYB.
VNThCh 'aThV LNThChYV V'aTh-Ur'aShV V'aTh-PhDUrV V'yUrK HKHN 'aThM 'yL-H'yTShYM 'aShUr 'yL-H'aSh 'aShUr 'yL-HMZBCh.
VHQUrB VHKUr'yYM YUrChTSh BMYM VHQUrYB HKHN 'aTh-HKL VHQTYUr HMZBChH 'yLH HV'a 'aShH UrYCh NYChCh LYHVH.
V'aM MN-H'yVPh 'yLH QUrBNV LYHVH VHQUrYB MN-HThUrYM 'aV MN-BNY HYVNH 'aTh-QUrBNV.
VHQUrYBV HKHN 'aL-HMZBCh VMLQ 'aTh-Ur'aShV VHQTYUr HMZBChH VNMTShH DMV 'yL QYUr HMZBCh.
VHSYUr 'aTh-MUr'aThV BNTShThH VHShLYK 'aThH 'aTShL HMZBCh QDMH 'aL-MQVM HDShN.
VShS'y 'aThV BKNPhYV L'a YBDYL VHQTYUr 'aThV HKHN HMZBChH 'yL-H'yTShYM 'aShUr 'yL-H'aSh 'yLH HV'a 'aShH UrYCh NYChCh LYHVH.
